{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"82492a728c","title":"关于彭真的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ddd93667be","index":0,"year":1966,"month":4,"day":29,"articleId":"82492a728c","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"彭真","id":"5fd56865b0","type":"人物"},{"name":"各级党政领导人","id":"a59dfa2519","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"95f0eb1ebe","type":"title","text":"关于彭真的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82492a728c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bee23717dc","type":"paragraph","text":"关于彭真的谈话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82492a728c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ec5fd75b3b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82492a728c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"551cd4d8ed","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.04.29","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82492a728c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b30782b2b3","type":"paragraph","text":"北京一根针也插不进去，一滴水也滴不进去。彭真要按他的世界观改造党，事物是向他的反面发展的，他自己为自己准备了垮台的条件。这是必然的事，是从偶然中暴露出来的，一步一步深入的。历史教训并不是人人都引以为戒的。这是阶级斗争的规律，是不以人们的意志为转移的。凡是在中央有人搞鬼，我就号召地方起来攻他们，叫孙悟空大闹大宫，并要搞那些保玉皇大帝的人。彭真是混到党内的渺小的人物，没有什么了不起，一个指头就捅倒地。“西风落叶下长安”，告诉同志们不要无穷地忧虑。灰尘不扫不走，阶级敌人不斗不倒。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82492a728c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c029b0d023","type":"paragraph","text":"赞成鲁迅的意见，经书不可不读，不可多读。不读人家会欺侮你。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82492a728c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7bed1d36a","type":"paragraph","text":"现象是看得见的，本质是隐蔽的。本质也会通过现象表现出来。彭真的本质隐藏了三十年。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82492a728c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4bf24ab22b","type":"paragraph","text":"要不要告诉阿尔巴尼亚同志？没有什么不可告人的！","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82492a728c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}